'''高乐高'''（Cola Cao）是首创于[[西班牙|西班牙]]的一种饮品，现在在[[高乐高#营销|多个国家或地区进行生产和销售]]。<ref name="Howse 2013">{{Cite book|title=The Train in Spain|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=afsJAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA21|publisher=A&C Black|date=2013-11-07|isbn=978-1-4411-2839-3|language=en|first=Christopher|last=Howse|access-date=2021-08-25|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825071922/https://books.google.com/books?id=afsJAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA21|dead-url=no}}</ref>主要成分有脱脂[[可可粉|可可粉]]、[[蔗糖|蔗糖]]、谷物粉（小麦粉、麦精及可拉果精粉）等。由西班牙{{Link-en|埃蒂利亚食品|Idilia Foods}}生产。<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Rise of Spanish Multinationals: European Business in the Global Economy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hOsiGt_VoAMC&pg=PA47|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2005-07-28|isbn=978-0-521-84721-6|language=en|first=Mauro|last=Guillén|access-date=2021-08-25|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825071920/https://books.google.com/books?id=hOsiGt_VoAMC&pg=PA47|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1990年，埃蒂利亚食品进入[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]，成为第一家进入中国大陆的西班牙食品企业。<ref>{{Cite web|title=高乐高colacao_高乐高 - 随心所欲“高乐高”|url=http://wap.ppsj.com.cn/pp/colacao.html|access-date=2021-08-25|work=wap.ppsj.com.cn|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825070842/http://wap.ppsj.com.cn/pp/colacao.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
