==原料==
高乐高使用[[糖|糖]]、加工[[可可豆|可可豆]]、[[麵粉|小麦粉]]和[[可乐果|可乐果]]制成，富含[[维生素|维生素]]、[[钙|钙]]和[[磷|磷]]。<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Breakfast Book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=P_k7pZg7tBQC&pg=PA94|publisher=Reaktion Books|date=2013-06-01|isbn=978-1-78023-121-1|language=en|first=Andrew|last=Dalby|access-date=2021-08-25|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825071921/https://books.google.com/books?id=P_k7pZg7tBQC&pg=PA94|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Cola Cao - Chocolate Powder calories, carbs & nutrition facts {{!}} MyFitnessPal|url=https://www.myfitnesspal.com/food/calories/cola-cao-chocolate-powder-391376819?v2=false|access-date=2021-08-25|work=www.myfitnesspal.com|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825081948/https://www.myfitnesspal.com/food/calories/cola-cao-chocolate-powder-391376819?v2=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==准备==
高乐高是一种粉末状的饮品。旨在与[[牛奶|牛奶]]混合，<ref name="Howse 2013"/>不过也可以与[[水|水]]或[[豆浆|豆浆]]混合。它也可以添加至早餐麦片中或可用作烘焙原料。特别在西班牙本土，高乐高是早餐或晚餐的流行搭配。<ref name="Howse 2013"/>
==分配==
高乐高装在各种尺寸的容器中出售。不过也以液体形式生产，并装在塑料瓶中。<ref name="Howse 2013"/>
==营销==
高乐高在多个国家进行营销，譬如[[西班牙|西班牙]]、[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]、[[智利|智利]]、[[波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那|波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那]]、[[日本|日本]]以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nutrexpa|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010629172047/http://www.nutrexpa.es/index.htm|access-date=2021-08-25|date=2001-06-29|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>
